tex3ds
------------------------------------------
3DS Texture Conversion

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.10-1
  libMagickC++7_5-7.1.2.11-1
  libfreetype6-2.13.3-1
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  autoconf-archive-2024.10.16-1
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  libMagick-devel-7.1.2.11-1
  libfreetype-devel-2.13.3-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/devkitPro/tex3ds

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/devkitPro/tex3ds/archive/refs/tags/v2.3.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack tex3ds-2.3.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./tex3ds-2.3.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/tex3ds-2.3.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/tex3ds-2.3.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(tex3ds)
  /usr/bin/mkbcfnt.exe
  /usr/bin/tex3ds.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/tex3ds.README
  /usr/share/doc/tex3ds/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/tex3ds/README.md

